This Resource describes the cycling power, which is the amount of
energy transferred or converted per unit time. The unit, which is the
default SI unit, is W (which is equal to one joule per second). The
power Property is a read-only value that is provided by the server.
When range (from "oic. r. baseresource") is omitted the default is 0
